data.description: Located in a quiet cul-de-sac in New Braunfels, you'll find this spacious five-bedroom home. Greeted by an inviting front porch, you'll walk into the formal living/dining combination and entry way. All living areas downstairs are covered with beautiful wood flooring. Get cozy in the large family room with the warm stone fireplace. The chef in the family will love the large granite island, upgraded cabinetry and stainless-steel appliances.  The bay windows in the primary bedroom bring in lots of natural light. The primary bath has a large walk-in shower and garden tub. Upstairs is equally as spacious with four bedrooms, a game room, and theater room. Outside is an entertainers dream with a covered patio and sparkling pool.  A peaceful park dedicated to only this neighborhood is within walking distance.
